V12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thu-th%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A3n-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-KhEUstEO-F5RP6p1mmqSjw">Thu thành vãn vọng - 秋城晚望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%B1-Nam-Khang-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-T%C3%ADn-ho%C3%A0n-quy%E1%BB%83n-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-2YZNqlcvqwLOxe36xP-K0Q">Tự Nam Khang vãng Quảng Tín hoàn quyển thuật hoài - 自南康往廣信完卷述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Chu-Trinh/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%C3%B4-m%C3%B4n/poem-cVkNAak-v8HIDIc9nZn87A">Xuất đô môn - 出都門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Chu-Trinh/author-WLQpVVlxI3bhRBsoRr4SCw">Phan Chu Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-qu%E1%BB%91c/poem-UK-2GvtOe_wbSd4b-DuJ7w">Xuất quốc - 出國</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-2WHplYhGibS3kNKVcV5ntg">Trần Ích Tắc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
